{
  "stem": "24130.6",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And they bombed the station.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And the, the train turned over.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So when the train turned over, the girls start running to, to, to look for-- we didn't know that in the back of the train, there are men.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So they start running to find out, where are you from?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Where are you from?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And the nurse that was in Neustadt-- we had a nurse-- she found her husband there.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they left.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They ran away.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We found out after the war that they ran away from there.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And a lot of girls were bombed.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And, and they lost a limb, a hand, a foot.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They were bleeding.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And they would go to the soldiers and say, please just shoot me.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They were in such a pain.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They said, your friends did it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Your American friends did it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So they-- it was just a terrible sight.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we were saved because our train, when, when turned over, we wound up underneath.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So from the bombs, the pieces didn't, didn't hurt us.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So we sisters were saved again.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then when the bombing was over, they turned over the train again.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we went back into the train.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we moved on.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we came to Bergen-Belsen.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
